\end_layout

\begin_layout Proposition
Any tensor constructed using a linear combination of 
\begin_inset Formula $K_{ijk}:=\partial_{i}g_{jk}$
\end_inset

 or its powers will be the trivial zero tensor.
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
\begin_inset Separator plain
\end_inset


\end_layout

