\begin_inset Formula $\mathcal{O}(\epsilon)$
\end_inset

 starting and ending at 
\begin_inset Formula $x_{(0)}$
\end_inset

 with 
\begin_inset Formula $n_{1}$
\end_inset

 an initial tangent vector (a vector in the tangent space at 
\begin_inset Formula $x_{(0)}$
\end_inset

) and 
\begin_inset Formula $n_{2}$
\end_inset

